avdta.dta

Class DTAResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.dta.DTAResults

  • public class DTAResults
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the results from running DTA. It includes the travel time, gap, and number of exiting vehicles. It is returned as an output from running DTA.
